long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Change default search engine to make Green Building Search your search in browser address bar (omnibox).
Green Building Search is a small and fast Google Chrome extension that helps you change your default search engine in address bar of the browser to Green Building Search very easily.
Just click on «Add to Chrome» and «Keep it» buttons (to leave the default search Green Building Search) and enjoy new search functionality.

Terms of Use: https://greenbuildingclub.com/terms.html
Privacy Policy: https://greenbuildingclub.com/privacy.html

By click on «Add to Chrome» button and installing the Green Building Search extension, you are agreeing to install this extension, you are agreeing Privacy Policy, and you are agreeing Terms of Use.
